### Step 7: `compiler.rs` 수정 — Identifier/Let 완성

**구조체 변경:**
```rust
use std::collections::HashMap;
pub struct Compiler {
    bytecode: Bytecode,
    pub debug_mode: bool,
    locals: HashMap<String, usize>,  // [NEW] 변수명 → 슬롯 인덱스
    next_local: usize,               // [NEW] 다음 슬롯 번호 (0부터 시작)
}
```

**Statement::Let 수정:**
```rust
Statement::Let { name, value } => {
    self.compile_expression(value)?;           // 스택에 값 푸시
    let idx = self.next_local;
    self.locals.insert(name.clone(), idx);
    self.next_local += 1;
    self.emit_with_byte_operand(OpCode::OpSetLocal, idx as u8); // 팝→로컬 저장
}
```

**Expression::Identifier 수정 (`"not yet implemented"` 제거):**
```rust
Expression::Identifier(name) => {
    match self.locals.get(name) {
        Some(&idx) => self.emit_with_byte_operand(OpCode::OpGetLocal, idx as u8),
        None => return Err(format!("Undefined variable: '{}'", name)),
    }
}
```

**신규 메서드:**
```rust
fn emit_with_byte_operand(&mut self, op: OpCode, operand: u8) {
    self.emit(op);
    self.bytecode.add_instruction(operand);  // 1바이트 (opcode.rs: width=1)
}
pub fn local_count(&self) -> usize { self.next_local }
pub fn get_local_index(&self, name: &str) -> Option<usize> { self.locals.get(name).copied() }
```

> **근거**: `opcode.rs`에서 `OpGetLocal.operand_width() = 1` → u8 사용, 최대 256 변수

