### Step 8: `vm.rs` 수정 — 로컬 변수 실행

**구조체 변경:**
```rust
pub struct VM {
    bytecode: Bytecode,
    stack: Vec<Value>,
    ip: usize,
    heap: ObjectHeap,
    locals: Vec<Value>,  // [NEW] 256 슬롯 (사전 초기화)
}
// VM::new()에서: locals: vec![Value::Null; 256]
```

**신규 OpCode 처리 (`_ => return Err` 대신):**
```rust
OpCode::OpSetLocal => {
    let idx = self.read_u8() as usize;
    let val = self.stack_pop()?;   // 팝 후 저장 (Statement 의미론)
    self.locals[idx] = val;
}
OpCode::OpGetLocal => {
    let idx = self.read_u8() as usize;
    self.stack.push(self.locals[idx].clone());
}
fn read_u8(&mut self) -> u8 {
    let b = self.bytecode.instructions[self.ip]; self.ip += 1; b
}
```

